Package: BayesOmics
Title: Bayesian differential analysis for omics data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Térence", "Viellard", , "terence.viellard@gmx.fr", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Bayesian differential analysis for omics data.The correlation structure is captured by a kernel. Users need to choose a kernel, optimize the hyperparameters, and then use the correlation matrix computed by this kernel in the analysis.
